This application can be represented as a social platform so that users with diet and nutrition coaches can engage together with more nutrition tips.
This application narrow down tha user to specific segment like setting a small goal for everyday so that user can reach a routine diet.
This application can also recommend the personalized meal plans and healthy recipes using nutrition tracking tools.
This applaication can be connected to other devices like smart watch so that it can monitor water intake, calories, blood sugar level and other health conditions.
